<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 01:08:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Kalshi 获得向专业人士提供保证金交易的许可</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-27/kalshi-approved-for-margin-trading-as-it-lures-wall-street-pros</link><description>Kalshi Inc. 已获得许可证，允许其向用户提供保证金交易，这一功能将使预测市场平台对成熟的机构投资者更具吸引力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i9bau6RgdjV8/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 18:33:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-27/kalshi-approved-for-margin-trading-as-it-lures-wall-street-pros</guid></item><item><title>随着期权指向更深层次的下跌，比特币继续下滑</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-27/bitcoin-slumps-with-options-showing-traders-turning-defensive</link><description>由于今年最大的期权到期后交易者转向防御，而投资者继续从加密货币交易所交易基金中撤资，比特币跌至三周多以来的最低水平。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iqBaYVLFGHv4/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 11:43:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-27/bitcoin-slumps-with-options-showing-traders-turning-defensive</guid></item><item><title>加密货币交易者正在转变为大型跨资产追逐者</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-24/crypto-perps-platforms-are-increasingly-used-for-trading-tradfi-assets</link><description>Hyperliquid、Ostium 等网站发现传统资产永续资产占据了更大的交易量份额&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iViar1s5soj4/v9/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-24/crypto-perps-platforms-are-increasingly-used-for-trading-tradfi-assets</guid></item><item><title>参议员询问比特大陆相关的“国家安全担忧”</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-27/senator-asks-about-bitmain-related-national-security-concerns</link><description>彭博新闻社去年 11 月报道称，一家中国比特币挖矿制造商已成为联邦调查的焦点，之后，一名民主党参议员向美国商务部索取有关如何解决该公司所造成的“潜在国家安全问题”的信息。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iBrixsrWLeqk/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 16:16:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-27/senator-asks-about-bitmain-related-national-security-concerns</guid></item><item><title>加密“保险”可能无法保护您免遭盗窃</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-27/crypto-theft-fuels-insurance-boom-but-protections-vary</link><description>当 Matthew Allan 意识到他的 Coinbase 账户中缺少近 10 万美元的比特币时，他并不太担心。他已经注册了 Coinbase One，每月订阅费用为 29.99 美元，承诺提供高达 100 万美元的账户保护。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3FMaHzW1L_A/v0/1200x-1.gif" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 11:30:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-27/crypto-theft-fuels-insurance-boom-but-protections-vary</guid></item><item><title>中东动荡加剧，比特币面临 140 亿美元期权到期</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-26/bitcoin-faces-14-billion-options-expiry-while-middle-east-turmoil-mounts</link><description>比特币今年最大的期权到期正与地缘政治波动相冲突，地缘政治波动没有显示出放松迹象，和平谈判的成败也不确定。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iFsaijb3rEV4/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 16:55:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-26/bitcoin-faces-14-billion-options-expiry-while-middle-east-turmoil-mounts</guid></item><item><title>币安澳大利亚实体因错误分类零售客户而被罚款</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-27/binance-australia-entity-fined-for-misclassifying-retail-clients</link><description>澳大利亚法院对币安澳大利亚衍生品公司处以 1000 万澳元（690 万美元）的罚款，原因是入职失败导致客户损失和费用达数百万美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iHj7PSpMqi.4/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 09:05:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-27/binance-australia-entity-fined-for-misclassifying-retail-clients</guid></item><item><title>为了稳定币的可靠性，加密货币风投正在放弃 Web3</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-26/crypto-vcs-are-abandoning-web3-for-the-dependability-of-stablecoins</link><description>金融管道是吸引风投投资加密货币的原因。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iexkq.SsWdbI/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-26/crypto-vcs-are-abandoning-web3-for-the-dependability-of-stablecoins</guid></item><item><title>Saylor表示零售业拥有Strategy高收益证券80%的股份</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-26/michael-saylor-says-retail-own-80-of-strategy-s-high-yielding-preferred-shares</link><description>散户投资者显然还没有放弃迈克尔·塞勒 (Michael Saylor) 的梦想，即让比特币成为卓越的价值储存手段。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iataR.FPvUqo/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 19:16:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-26/michael-saylor-says-retail-own-80-of-strategy-s-high-yielding-preferred-shares</guid></item><item><title>加密货币通过符合 FNMA 资格的贷款进入抵押贷款市场</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-26/crypto-enters-the-mortgage-market-via-fannie-mae-eligible-loans</link><description>加密货币正在深入美国金融体系——这一次是通过抵押贷款市场。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i5NvLZHuAyhA/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 13:10:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-26/crypto-enters-the-mortgage-market-via-fannie-mae-eligible-loans</guid></item></channel></rss>